During the bulk rebase of 38 Mnemosyne skill PRs:
1. After PR #1441 landed markdownlint/pixi-check jobs, 11 skill PRs immediately failed CI due to
   pre-existing violations in .claude/plugins/ (not the PRs themselves). Pattern: fix root cause
   on main first, then rebase PRs.
2. PRs 1438 and 1440 both proposed v2.9.0 of batch-pr-rebase-workflow.md with different content.
